OL,3,CNew watchdog could force owners to
OL,4,Csell troubled clubs
OL,6,FThe chairman of a new football
OL,7,Fwatchdog says he is seeking powers to
OL,8,Finvestigate troubled clubs like
OL,9,FSheffield Wednesday - and could force
OL,10,Fowners to sell as a "last resort".
OL,12,FDavid Kogan, who was appointed to the
OL,13,FIndependent Football Regulator on
OL,14,FMonday, said Wednesday's situation is
OL,15,Fa "significant problem" for football.
