OL,3,CNew watchdog could force owners to
OL,4,Csell troubled clubs
OL,6,FThe club has been placed under a
OL,7,Fnumber of transfer embargoes for tax
OL,8,Fdebts. It has also failed to pay
OL,9,Fplayers and staff on time on five
OL,10,Fseparate occasions this year,
OL,11,Fincluding last month.
OL,13,FWednesday's owner, Dejphon Chansiri,
OL,14,Fwho took over in 2015, has faced
OL,15,Fcriticism for failing to secure a deal
OL,16,Fafter saying he would be willing to
OL,17,Fsell the club.
