OL,3,CNew watchdog could force owners to
OL,4,Csell troubled clubs
OL,6,FA number of first-team players and
OL,7,Fcoaches, including former manager
OL,8,FDanny Rohl, have since left
OL,9,FHillsborough, leaving the Owls with a
OL,10,Fthreadbare squad and backroom staff.
OL,12,FThey face a possible points deduction
OL,13,Fbecause of the ongoing financial
OL,14,Fissues.
OL,16,FNow the regulator wants to be able to
OL,17,Ftake action against clubs in such
OL,18,Fsituations, which could include
OL,19,Fforcing unsuitable owners to sell
OL,20,Ffootball clubs.
