OL,3,CNew watchdog could force owners to
OL,4,Csell troubled clubs
OL,6,FKogan said it would be the "last
OL,7,Fresort."
OL,9,F"Clearly Sheffield Wednesday has been
OL,10,Fa significant problem for the EFL and
OL,11,Fa significant problem for football,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"If your question is, 'would we
OL,15,Fintervene in the final instance?', the
OL,16,Fanswer is once we gather the evidence
OL,17,Fand know what's going on, we will.
