OL,6,F"It's a last resort (forcing a sale)
OL,7,Fbecause the last thing we want to do
OL,8,Fis start getting involved with an
OL,9,Findividual club, an individual owner,
OL,10,Fwithout being able to work with that
OL,11,Fowner to try and resolve the issues
OL,12,Fthat the club's facing and the owner's
OL,13,Ffacing."
OL,15,FHe also expressed sympathy with the
OL,16,FOwls as he met four supporter groups.
OL,18,FWednesday sit second bottom of the Sky
OL,19,FBet Championship table with six points
OL,20,Ffrom nine games.
