OL,3,CNew watchdog could force owners to
OL,4,Csell troubled clubs
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the union, Unite, said
OL,7,Fworkers would be taking action against
OL,8,FChansiri for repeatedly failing to pay
OL,9,Fthe club's non-football staff.
OL,11,FThe union's regional officer, Daniel
OL,12,FGawthorpe, said low paid staff are
OL,13,Fbeing forced to take out loans or
OL,14,Fborrow from family to cover their
OL,15,Fbills.
OL,17,F"These workers have had enough. They
OL,18,Ftotally dedicated to the club but
OL,19,Ftheir loyalty is being taken advantage
OL,20,Fof.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
